WEBVTT

01:42.780 --> 01:46.030
[Love Song in Winter]

01:46.100 --> 01:48.990
[Episode 23]

01:51.110 --> 01:51.789
Dr. Lu,

01:51.789 --> 01:52.930
thank you for today.

01:52.990 --> 01:53.870
Will it delay your work?

01:53.950 --> 01:54.590
No.

01:54.630 --> 01:56.240
I'm off today.

01:56.430 --> 01:57.590
I haven't skated for a long time.

01:57.710 --> 01:59.250
Just think of it as Xiaoman playing with me.

01:59.360 --> 02:00.660
Thank you so much.

02:01.430 --> 02:02.390
Listen to Dr. Lu later,

02:02.390 --> 02:02.870
understand?

02:02.870 --> 02:03.470
Okay.

02:04.420 --> 02:05.060
Xiaoman.

02:05.190 --> 02:05.870
Are you ready?

02:05.910 --> 02:06.790
Yes.

02:06.910 --> 02:07.350
Let's go.

02:07.430 --> 02:08.039
Go.

03:07.070 --> 03:07.890
Keep going.

03:08.110 --> 03:09.600
Keep going and you're halfway there.

03:10.230 --> 03:11.630
Just skate a bit more. You'll get it.

03:11.750 --> 03:12.550
Xiaoman.

03:12.630 --> 03:13.470
Mr. Wen!

03:14.100 --> 03:15.160
Why are you here?

03:15.950 --> 03:16.790
I'm sorry, Xiaoman.

03:16.810 --> 03:18.470
I was too busy yesterday,

03:18.510 --> 03:19.400
but I took

03:19.400 --> 03:20.670
the earliest flight today.

03:21.550 --> 03:22.550
Are you angry?

03:22.590 --> 03:23.240
No.

03:23.290 --> 03:23.920
Ms. Lu

03:23.950 --> 03:25.230
played with me for a long time.

03:26.300 --> 03:26.880
Mr. Wen,

03:26.910 --> 03:28.230
can you skate too?

03:29.550 --> 03:30.980
I'm not good at skating.

03:31.110 --> 03:31.660
Can you...

03:31.750 --> 03:32.800
Can you hold my hand?

03:33.390 --> 03:33.829
Sure.

03:33.910 --> 03:35.190
All three of us can skate together.

04:12.790 --> 04:13.440
Thank you.

04:13.470 --> 04:14.030
It's okay.

04:14.110 --> 04:15.070
Let them play.

04:17.860 --> 04:20.070
Mr. Wen, look, I can skate!

04:21.190 --> 04:21.550
Yes.

04:21.579 --> 04:22.360
You're skating fast.

04:22.750 --> 04:23.630
Yes.

04:34.340 --> 04:36.090
You're really fast now.

04:56.350 --> 04:57.140
Are you happy today?

04:57.270 --> 04:58.070
Yes.

04:58.360 --> 04:59.150
I saw a kid

04:59.180 --> 04:59.950
who was amazing.

04:59.980 --> 05:01.550
He kept spinning inside.

05:02.670 --> 05:03.160
Come.

05:03.270 --> 05:03.790
Say thank you.

05:03.820 --> 05:04.580
Thank Ms. Lu

05:04.600 --> 05:05.260
and Mr. Wen.

05:05.430 --> 05:06.240
Thank you, Ms. Lu.

05:06.270 --> 05:07.230
Thank you, Mr. Wen.

05:07.310 --> 05:08.520
Thank you for today.

05:08.710 --> 05:09.840
Ms. Lu, Mr. Wen,

05:09.870 --> 05:10.310
can we

05:10.390 --> 05:11.760
play again in the future?

05:11.800 --> 05:12.510
Xiaoman.

05:13.310 --> 05:15.540
If you go back and listen to your mom

05:15.670 --> 05:16.980
to eat well, exercise well,

05:17.070 --> 05:18.110
and do check-ups,

05:18.270 --> 05:19.940
Ms. Lu and I

05:20.000 --> 05:20.880
will take you out.

05:20.990 --> 05:21.720
Okay?

05:21.740 --> 05:22.310
Really,

05:22.350 --> 05:23.270
Ms. Lu?

05:26.060 --> 05:27.120
I'm in the hospital.

05:27.150 --> 05:28.450
When you go for a check-up,

05:28.510 --> 05:29.360
I'll wait for you in the hospital.

05:29.390 --> 05:30.000
Okay?

05:30.110 --> 05:30.910
Sure.

05:31.430 --> 05:31.870
Alright.

05:31.950 --> 05:32.830
It's almost time.

05:32.870 --> 05:33.790
We're leaving.

05:33.909 --> 05:34.950
-Thank you.
-I’ll get someone to give you a ride.

05:35.150 --> 05:35.680
No need.

05:35.710 --> 05:36.900
We can go back by ourselves.

05:36.920 --> 05:37.680
It's okay, miss.

05:37.830 --> 05:38.930
Mr. Wen has arranged everything.

05:38.950 --> 05:39.800
Let me see you off.

05:40.270 --> 05:41.120
I'm sorry.

05:41.230 --> 05:41.970
Thank you.

05:42.030 --> 05:42.600
Bye.

05:42.630 --> 05:43.300
-Bye.
-Bye.

05:43.330 --> 05:44.020
Bye.

05:46.730 --> 05:47.950
I'm going home too.

05:48.920 --> 05:49.570
Lu Yan.

05:52.030 --> 05:52.909
It's still early.

05:52.909 --> 05:54.800
Let's have dinner together.

05:55.470 --> 05:57.400
I agreed to go home and eat with Jiang Chengyi.

05:57.510 --> 05:58.360
See you.

05:59.720 --> 06:00.380
Lu Yan.

06:05.390 --> 06:05.990
Actually,

06:06.030 --> 06:07.310
I have a question for you.

06:11.340 --> 06:12.770
Jiang Chengyi and I are the same age.

06:13.470 --> 06:14.270
Why don't you call him

06:14.310 --> 06:15.420
your senior?

06:17.430 --> 06:19.560
I never thought about this.

06:19.730 --> 06:22.340
Maybe I'm used to it.

06:25.950 --> 06:26.480
Do you know

06:26.510 --> 06:27.790
how long we've known each other for?

06:31.190 --> 06:32.470
A long time.

06:33.150 --> 06:34.270
Ten years and three months.

06:38.030 --> 06:39.230
We met each other during the Mid-Autumn Festival

06:39.250 --> 06:40.790
in 2014.

06:42.630 --> 06:43.550
I knew you

06:44.510 --> 06:46.270
before Jiang Chengyi knew you.

06:52.909 --> 06:54.530
We were from the same department.

06:54.909 --> 06:55.990
We graduated under

06:56.070 --> 06:56.790
the same mentor.

06:57.870 --> 06:58.870
Jiang Chengyi left you

06:58.909 --> 07:00.000
for eight years.

07:00.030 --> 07:01.560
You lost contact,

07:01.990 --> 07:03.540
while we met often.

07:04.030 --> 07:04.990
We should be

07:05.030 --> 07:05.790
more familiar with

07:05.790 --> 07:07.070
and know each other better, right?

07:07.710 --> 07:08.670
Senior.

07:10.810 --> 07:11.680
Perhaps

07:13.950 --> 07:14.750
you don't have to

07:14.750 --> 07:15.750
call me senior.

07:18.140 --> 07:18.910
I...

07:22.110 --> 07:22.790
I...

07:23.230 --> 07:25.390
I don't understand what you mean.

07:25.390 --> 07:26.080
But

07:26.550 --> 07:27.650
I've always

07:27.740 --> 07:29.270
viewed you as my senior.

07:31.150 --> 07:31.710
Lu Yan.

07:33.790 --> 07:35.740
There's something

07:35.830 --> 07:36.950
I forgot to tell you.

07:39.930 --> 07:41.960
Jiang Chengyi and I have officially made up.

07:47.159 --> 07:48.260
I'm leaving.

08:06.130 --> 08:07.760
The cunning rabbit has three caves.

08:08.570 --> 08:10.720
Li Ruonan has this den too.

08:24.950 --> 08:25.470
Yue.

08:26.630 --> 08:27.370
What's going on?

08:28.030 --> 08:29.600
It's where Li Ruonan lived,

08:29.990 --> 08:30.550
but

08:30.630 --> 08:31.950
besides these daily necessities,

08:31.990 --> 08:33.580
there are not many valuable clues.

08:33.720 --> 08:34.409
What about the phone?

08:34.710 --> 08:35.230
No.

08:35.690 --> 08:36.740
There's only one power bank.

08:39.429 --> 08:40.549
We're too late.

08:43.950 --> 08:44.910
Here, tracing team.

08:45.350 --> 08:45.830
Please work hard

08:45.870 --> 08:47.140
and search this place again.

08:47.230 --> 08:48.480
Let's focus on

08:48.510 --> 08:49.630
all traces from people

08:49.670 --> 08:51.430
other than Li Ruonan.

08:51.600 --> 08:52.030
Okay?

08:52.110 --> 08:52.790
Come on.

08:53.260 --> 08:53.830
Okay.

08:57.400 --> 09:00.150
[Anshan, Ninghai Public Security
Criminal Investigation Unit]

09:03.750 --> 09:04.850
It seems that

09:05.310 --> 09:06.160
someone came

09:06.190 --> 09:07.310
before us.

09:08.260 --> 09:09.510
What should we do, Senior?

09:09.590 --> 09:10.230
Next...

09:10.910 --> 09:11.590
Since they

09:11.630 --> 09:13.460
dared to take the phone,

09:14.350 --> 09:15.670
that means there's someone

09:15.710 --> 09:16.670
behind Li Ruonan.

09:20.240 --> 09:21.590
Let them come back first.

09:22.190 --> 09:22.830
It's okay.

09:22.910 --> 09:23.820
All of them?

09:24.070 --> 09:24.900
All of them.

09:25.190 --> 09:25.750
Captain Jiang,

09:25.870 --> 09:27.400
this is the file from Deng Man's case that you wanted.

09:27.470 --> 09:28.390
Okay, thank you.

09:29.310 --> 09:30.030
Deng Man?

09:51.910 --> 09:53.070
Jiang Chengyi,

09:53.150 --> 09:54.720
I want to tell you something.

09:54.990 --> 09:55.590
What is it?

09:56.350 --> 09:57.180
Well,

09:57.790 --> 09:58.440
didn't I take Xiaoman

09:58.470 --> 10:00.080
skating today?

10:00.230 --> 10:01.230
Then,

10:01.510 --> 10:03.120
Wen Peng said he wouldn't go,

10:03.270 --> 10:04.390
but he ended up going.

10:07.860 --> 10:09.310
He asked you out on purpose.

10:11.450 --> 10:13.870
I thought he was taking Xiaoman.

10:14.810 --> 10:16.120
But he asked you out instead.

10:16.790 --> 10:17.390
Right?

10:18.390 --> 10:19.360
So, then what?

10:19.390 --> 10:20.190
What do you want to say?

10:21.230 --> 10:22.140
Then...

10:23.230 --> 10:24.630
Then he just told me

10:24.630 --> 10:25.910
some

10:26.630 --> 10:28.230
ambiguous things.

10:28.300 --> 10:29.670
I think he was

10:29.670 --> 10:30.730
a little emotional.

10:31.030 --> 10:31.590
Emotional?

10:32.740 --> 10:33.790
What ambiguous things?

10:34.750 --> 10:35.830
He just said

10:36.110 --> 10:38.200
he wanted to take me out for dinner.

10:38.230 --> 10:39.740
What's wrong with that?

10:42.030 --> 10:42.740
What else?

10:42.990 --> 10:43.630
What else did he say

10:43.630 --> 10:44.510
that felt ambiguous?

10:45.990 --> 10:46.560
He said

10:46.590 --> 10:48.340
not to call him senior.

10:48.910 --> 10:49.670
What should you call him then?

10:49.950 --> 10:50.470
Pengpeng?

10:50.670 --> 10:52.040
Pengpeng?

10:52.310 --> 10:53.280
Call him Wen Peng.

10:53.310 --> 10:54.320
I'll call him by his full name.

10:54.350 --> 10:55.390
I think it's suitable.

10:56.230 --> 10:57.340
I think it's better

10:57.510 --> 10:58.550
to use his full name.

10:58.690 --> 10:59.610
Alright.

11:02.650 --> 11:04.850
And then I told him immediately

11:05.190 --> 11:06.630
that we've made up.

11:06.650 --> 11:07.880
Then I turned around and left.

11:08.030 --> 11:08.840
Really?

11:08.950 --> 11:10.020
So decisive.

11:10.050 --> 11:11.170
I never looked back.

11:11.840 --> 11:12.560
And then?

11:12.980 --> 11:14.070
Nothing else happened.

11:14.390 --> 11:14.990
I didn't even look back.

11:15.010 --> 11:16.340
He called my name, but I didn't look back.

11:16.630 --> 11:17.350
You should know

11:17.390 --> 11:18.570
what he meant, right?

11:19.070 --> 11:21.080
I know now.

11:21.150 --> 11:22.080
Then, do you know what to do

11:22.110 --> 11:22.660
in the future?

11:22.870 --> 11:23.630
I know.

11:24.790 --> 11:26.110
Give me a hug.

11:26.130 --> 11:26.950
Give me a hug.

11:26.970 --> 11:27.650
Go back first.

11:27.830 --> 11:28.590
We'll talk about it later.

11:39.400 --> 11:41.500
Jiang Chengyi and I have officially made up.

11:57.190 --> 11:57.790
Come in.

11:59.310 --> 11:59.970
Mr. Wen,

12:00.190 --> 12:01.190
someone named Yu Zheng…

12:01.210 --> 12:01.950
Mr. Wen.

12:07.630 --> 12:08.650
Mr. Wen,

12:08.830 --> 12:09.680
I’m sorry

12:09.710 --> 12:10.890
for disturbing you so late.

12:10.990 --> 12:11.710
No,

12:11.870 --> 12:12.670
it's just a small thing.

12:12.790 --> 12:13.660
Have a seat.

12:15.110 --> 12:15.790
Okay.

12:23.740 --> 12:24.600
What brings you here

12:24.630 --> 12:25.190
at this hour?

12:25.720 --> 12:26.440
I'm here

12:26.470 --> 12:27.750
for Yu Bofeng.

12:30.430 --> 12:31.210
You know,

12:31.270 --> 12:32.550
as a superstar,

12:32.590 --> 12:33.470
he attracts

12:33.500 --> 12:34.860
too much attention in school.

12:36.070 --> 12:37.220
Our students

12:37.310 --> 12:38.270
all got in

12:38.310 --> 12:39.630
with their own abilities.

12:40.320 --> 12:41.480
As an artist,

12:41.510 --> 12:42.750
I think Yu Bofeng

12:43.400 --> 12:44.990
has privileged treatment.

12:45.750 --> 12:46.750
He can simply come and go

12:46.790 --> 12:47.910
as he pleases.

12:48.120 --> 12:49.160
This makes it seem

12:49.190 --> 12:51.330
a bit unfair

12:51.670 --> 12:53.020
to the other students.

12:54.760 --> 12:56.740
The interview is over anyway.

12:57.590 --> 12:58.470
About

12:58.510 --> 12:59.460
Yu Bofeng

12:59.480 --> 13:01.400
attending classes…

13:03.430 --> 13:04.590
I understand what you mean.

13:04.830 --> 13:06.390
I'll tell him then.

13:06.990 --> 13:07.670
Sorry

13:07.690 --> 13:08.740
for the trouble.

13:09.140 --> 13:09.870
It's okay.

13:10.310 --> 13:11.430
Thank you, Mr. Wen.

13:13.030 --> 13:14.740
Professor Yu, are you here

13:14.910 --> 13:15.600
for personal

13:15.630 --> 13:16.670
or business matters?

13:17.940 --> 13:19.150
Is there any difference?

13:19.390 --> 13:20.150
You came last time

13:20.150 --> 13:21.960
because of Wang Qianqian's case.

13:22.910 --> 13:23.560
Because

13:23.590 --> 13:25.200
businessmen like us

13:25.310 --> 13:26.470
are particularly afraid of troubles.

13:29.500 --> 13:30.240
It seems that you

13:30.310 --> 13:31.650
have a prejudice

13:31.830 --> 13:32.790
against the police.

13:33.430 --> 13:34.010
No, no.

13:34.030 --> 13:34.950
That's not so.

13:35.150 --> 13:35.910
It's just that

13:35.950 --> 13:37.330
it's better safe than sorry.

13:37.510 --> 13:38.390
Please understand.

13:40.630 --> 13:41.510
I think that you

13:41.590 --> 13:42.710
worry too much.

13:43.630 --> 13:44.710
I'm here today

13:44.790 --> 13:46.030
to talk to you about

13:46.070 --> 13:47.470
Yu Bofeng's suspension.

13:50.950 --> 13:52.440
Speaking of Yu Bofeng,

13:52.510 --> 13:53.870
he surprised me.

13:54.990 --> 13:55.990
During this period,

13:56.030 --> 13:57.070
not only has he worked hard

13:57.070 --> 13:58.470
but also made some progress.

13:59.670 --> 14:00.830
In the recent practice questions,

14:00.870 --> 14:02.040
there was a very difficult

14:02.070 --> 14:03.510
criminal psychology question.

14:03.820 --> 14:04.990
He actually got it right.

14:06.930 --> 14:08.590
I even joked with him

14:08.890 --> 14:10.790
that those who can answer this question

14:11.140 --> 14:13.220
either learned criminal psychology before

14:14.150 --> 14:15.070
or

14:17.670 --> 14:18.750
actually are

14:18.790 --> 14:19.950
serial killers.

14:27.930 --> 14:29.170
Actually,

14:29.430 --> 14:30.590
I answered that question for him.

14:32.870 --> 14:33.980
To be honest,

14:34.070 --> 14:35.240
when I was in college,

14:35.270 --> 14:37.190
I took a criminal psychology class,

14:37.750 --> 14:38.880
but I was not gifted,

14:38.910 --> 14:40.030
so I gave up.

14:40.790 --> 14:41.740
That question

14:42.030 --> 14:43.510
left a deep impression.

14:48.310 --> 14:50.120
What a coincidence, Mr. Wen.

14:51.070 --> 14:52.840
The mental state of a researcher

14:52.950 --> 14:53.670
also helps me

14:53.750 --> 14:54.940
manage my artists.

14:55.190 --> 14:56.000
As you know,

14:56.110 --> 14:58.040
we have to manage people in this industry

14:58.110 --> 14:59.190
and people are the hardest to manage.

14:59.320 --> 15:00.790
So, learning more

15:00.870 --> 15:01.440
is good

15:01.470 --> 15:02.860
for both me and my company.

15:05.150 --> 15:05.970
Yes.

15:06.830 --> 15:08.110
Your industry

15:08.150 --> 15:09.290
must be very stressful.

15:09.330 --> 15:10.810
You have to meet a lot of people

15:10.910 --> 15:12.100
and talk about many things.

15:13.000 --> 15:14.300
Reading more psychology books

15:14.330 --> 15:14.890
is good.

15:15.310 --> 15:17.850
It's very helpful toward stabilizing

15:18.190 --> 15:19.200
one's emotions.

15:21.550 --> 15:22.800
You're right, Professor Yu.

15:28.390 --> 15:29.850
I won't disturb you further.

15:30.660 --> 15:31.550
In the future,

15:31.590 --> 15:32.350
if you need

15:32.390 --> 15:33.360
my help,

15:33.510 --> 15:34.400
contact me any time.

15:35.210 --> 15:35.710
Okay.

15:36.470 --> 15:37.480
Sorry for the trouble.

15:37.510 --> 15:38.470
No need to see me out.

15:38.750 --> 15:39.310
Bye.

15:39.590 --> 15:40.190
Bye.

16:00.150 --> 16:00.950
No, no, no.

16:01.190 --> 16:01.710
Yue.

16:01.750 --> 16:03.710
Look who's back.

16:04.190 --> 16:05.360
Who is this?

16:05.450 --> 16:06.870
Who is back?

16:06.630 --> 16:10.450
[Anshan Criminal Investigation]

16:07.840 --> 16:09.340
Quickly put me down!

16:09.660 --> 16:11.030
Our hero is back.

16:11.310 --> 16:11.990
Professor Yu, Captain Jiang.

16:12.090 --> 16:12.780
How is your recovery?

16:12.910 --> 16:13.380
I'm fine.

16:13.430 --> 16:14.410
I can work anytime.

16:14.430 --> 16:15.670
You can work anytime?

16:15.700 --> 16:16.780
Stop messing with him.

16:16.950 --> 16:17.960
No hurry.

16:18.190 --> 16:19.440
Everyone,

16:19.470 --> 16:20.270
put your work aside.

16:20.550 --> 16:21.700
It's mealtime.

16:22.070 --> 16:22.870
Let's eat together.

16:23.090 --> 16:25.230
Great!

16:25.310 --> 16:25.870
Okay, Captain Jiang.

16:25.350 --> 16:25.810
[Anshan Criminal Investigation]

16:25.950 --> 16:26.700
Thank you, Captain Jiang.

16:26.790 --> 16:27.510
If you didn’t get stabbed,

16:27.510 --> 16:28.310
we wouldn't have

16:28.310 --> 16:29.030
this meal.

16:29.030 --> 16:29.510
Let's go.

16:29.830 --> 16:30.230
By the way,

16:30.500 --> 16:31.360
I have something to ask you.

16:31.910 --> 16:32.430
What's wrong?

16:33.110 --> 16:34.350
Wen Peng

16:34.430 --> 16:35.830
is your college classmate, right?

16:37.030 --> 16:38.510
We are

16:38.990 --> 16:39.670
schoolmates.

16:40.310 --> 16:41.240
We weren't in the same department.

16:43.350 --> 16:43.910
What's wrong?

16:44.830 --> 16:46.110
I don't think he's simple.

16:48.310 --> 16:49.110
Why not?

16:52.040 --> 16:53.030
Do you have time

16:53.070 --> 16:54.110
for lunch together?

16:54.510 --> 16:55.670
About what happened last time,

16:55.790 --> 16:57.270
I want to explain it to you in person.

17:06.670 --> 17:07.190
Mr. Wen.

17:07.920 --> 17:08.890
Mr. Zhong is here.

17:09.630 --> 17:10.119
Peng.

17:10.270 --> 17:10.829
Mr. Wen.

17:11.109 --> 17:11.589
Have a seat.

17:12.599 --> 17:13.270
Mr. Zhong,

17:13.390 --> 17:14.569
the contract has been printed.

17:14.589 --> 17:15.339
Please have a look.

17:16.720 --> 17:17.810
Mr. Wen, with our relationship,

17:17.839 --> 17:18.640
there's no need to review the contract.

17:18.670 --> 17:19.270
I'll just sign it directly.

17:19.270 --> 17:20.300
No, Zhong.

17:20.510 --> 17:21.770
Let Mr. Lu have a look.

17:22.990 --> 17:24.069
Lu is right.

17:24.170 --> 17:25.310
We must be careful

17:25.339 --> 17:26.310
with a contract worth millions.

17:29.190 --> 17:30.530
The filming will start next month?

17:31.440 --> 17:32.730
The male and female leads have been decided.

17:32.750 --> 17:33.300
So,

17:33.330 --> 17:34.660
we must start filming next month.

17:35.080 --> 17:35.680
Peng,

17:36.230 --> 17:37.820
are you in a hurry?

17:40.430 --> 17:41.470
I'm not,

17:41.670 --> 17:42.890
but Mr. Ke is.

17:43.330 --> 17:43.950
This morning,

17:43.990 --> 17:44.930
he called me

17:45.150 --> 17:47.200
and said he's negotiated for it to hit theaters

17:47.590 --> 17:48.430
during the Spring Festival.

17:49.790 --> 17:51.030
This industry is like this.

17:51.530 --> 17:52.480
The schedule comes first.

17:52.550 --> 17:53.310
As for the rest,

17:53.430 --> 17:54.390
they're lower priority.

17:54.950 --> 17:55.550
Indeed.

17:55.670 --> 17:56.590
Timing is the most important.

17:56.680 --> 17:57.850
Start it sooner, finish it sooner.

17:58.310 --> 17:59.070
Zhong, I've reviewed it.

17:59.150 --> 17:59.990
The contract is fine.

18:00.110 --> 18:01.030
Let's sign it.

18:05.890 --> 18:07.410
I told you there'd be no problems.

18:11.020 --> 18:12.330
[Signature: Wen Peng]

18:12.400 --> 18:14.430
[Signature: Zhong Wenxuan]

18:30.740 --> 18:32.430
Wish us a pleasant cooperation.

18:33.470 --> 18:34.110
In three days,

18:34.150 --> 18:35.410
the money will be transferred to the public account.

18:36.570 --> 18:37.410
Thank you, Mr. Wen.

18:43.790 --> 18:48.810
[Office of Criminal Investigation Unit]

18:44.210 --> 18:45.000
Anyway, that's basically

18:45.000 --> 18:46.270
what happened.

18:46.830 --> 18:47.500
I didn't expect

18:47.500 --> 18:48.550
he could solve that question.

18:49.070 --> 18:50.580
Do you think he's suspicious?

18:51.610 --> 18:52.750
A psychological test question

18:52.830 --> 18:54.020
doesn't prove anything,

18:54.590 --> 18:55.430
but

18:55.460 --> 18:56.670
he must be mentally unstable.

18:57.340 --> 18:58.210
I know about that.

18:58.730 --> 19:01.230
He was always beaten by his father when he was young.

19:01.610 --> 19:02.890
Lu Yan told me.

19:03.750 --> 19:04.510
No wonder.

19:05.310 --> 19:11.340
[Anshan, Ninghai Public Security
Criminal Investigation Unit]

19:05.990 --> 19:07.430
But judging from

19:07.710 --> 19:09.190
the relationships,

19:09.670 --> 19:11.230
he had something to do with

19:11.420 --> 19:12.870
Deng Man, Wang Qianqian,

19:13.670 --> 19:14.590
and Ding Jing.

19:16.980 --> 19:21.080
[Anshan, Ninghai Public Security
Criminal Investigation Unit]

19:17.430 --> 19:18.000
How about this?

19:18.550 --> 19:19.470
I'll find a chance

19:19.930 --> 19:21.230
to talk more with him.

19:21.710 --> 19:23.200
No, I'll go.

19:23.310 --> 19:24.810
His artist,

19:24.950 --> 19:25.750
Yu Bofeng,

19:25.790 --> 19:27.290
is in my class, right?

19:27.830 --> 19:28.630
I have more reasons

19:28.670 --> 19:29.790
to contact Wen Peng.

19:30.310 --> 19:31.820
Plus, you're too big of a target.

19:31.910 --> 19:33.390
He must be wary of you.

19:34.750 --> 19:36.230
I'll let you know immediately

19:36.310 --> 19:37.510
if I find any new clues.

19:38.230 --> 19:38.630
Okay.

19:38.950 --> 19:39.950
You are more suitable than me.

19:40.910 --> 19:41.640
Enjoy your noodles.

19:41.670 --> 19:42.410
I won't go.

19:42.470 --> 19:43.070
I have class.

19:43.190 --> 19:43.710
Okay.

19:43.790 --> 19:44.350
Bye.

19:43.910 --> 19:48.900
[Anshan, Ninghai Public Security
Criminal Investigation Unit]

19:44.430 --> 19:44.870
Bye.

19:49.040 --> 19:49.900
Hello, Professor Yu.

19:50.030 --> 19:50.840
I'm discharged.

19:50.870 --> 19:52.270
Do you have many classes this afternoon?

19:53.430 --> 19:54.080
Bofeng.

19:54.110 --> 19:55.160
Your discharge paperwork is all done.

19:56.470 --> 19:58.020
Mr. Wen instructed you to go to the company

19:58.050 --> 19:58.640
directly after you're discharged.

19:58.700 --> 19:59.430
He needs to see you.

19:59.750 --> 20:00.750
I'm not going to the company.

20:00.770 --> 20:01.740
I have something to do this afternoon.

20:01.950 --> 20:04.080
But Mr. Wen specifically instructed…

20:04.440 --> 20:05.170
Don’t worry.

20:05.310 --> 20:06.350
Help me deliver the things.

20:06.440 --> 20:07.250
Take the afternoon off.

20:07.500 --> 20:08.020
Okay.

20:22.180 --> 20:24.570
[Office]

20:24.040 --> 20:24.670
Professor Yu.

20:26.830 --> 20:27.630
Yu Bofeng.

20:28.580 --> 20:29.600
Why are you here?

20:29.630 --> 20:30.520
You've recovered?

20:29.720 --> 20:39.320
[Office]

20:30.990 --> 20:32.030
Pretty much.

20:33.140 --> 20:34.480
Why did you change your office?

20:34.790 --> 20:36.510
The teaching building is under renovation.

20:36.830 --> 20:37.430
Come in.

20:41.120 --> 20:42.500
Since you've recovered,

20:42.550 --> 20:44.240
why don't you go home and rest?

20:44.310 --> 20:45.270
Why did you come to school?

20:49.590 --> 20:50.720
You gave me

20:51.060 --> 20:52.590
a set of questions in the hospital, right?

20:52.870 --> 20:53.960
Although I made a lot of mistakes,

20:54.110 --> 20:55.470
I noted down all the answers.

20:55.590 --> 20:56.240
Now that I'm discharged,

20:56.270 --> 20:57.710
I want another set from you.

20:57.910 --> 20:58.860
I'll go back and study it.

21:02.030 --> 21:03.420
You're quite a hard worker.

21:03.510 --> 21:05.030
You want to study as soon as you get out of the hospital.

21:09.230 --> 21:10.130
How about this?

21:11.710 --> 21:12.830
I'll get you a set of books

21:12.950 --> 21:14.630
and prepare two question sets for you.

21:14.790 --> 21:15.700
Take them back

21:15.830 --> 21:16.990
and study them well by yourself.

21:17.390 --> 21:17.870
Okay?

21:26.750 --> 21:27.350
Professor Yu,

21:27.470 --> 21:28.480
to be honest,

21:28.510 --> 21:30.380
my interview

21:30.470 --> 21:31.270
already ended.

21:33.830 --> 21:34.510
I know.

21:35.750 --> 21:36.590
How did you know?

21:37.360 --> 21:38.860
It was on the news.

21:38.910 --> 21:39.940
The results were announced.

21:43.840 --> 21:45.160
I think

21:45.190 --> 21:46.810
you work quite hard

21:47.150 --> 21:49.540
and really want to learn something.

21:49.720 --> 21:51.310
As a teacher,

21:51.630 --> 21:52.890
I have no reason to reject you.

21:58.970 --> 22:00.150
Professor Yu,

22:00.350 --> 22:00.950
actually...

22:03.360 --> 22:04.330
Stop it.

22:04.950 --> 22:05.630
I know.

22:06.370 --> 22:07.180
How do you know again?

22:10.150 --> 22:10.990
You like me.

22:15.870 --> 22:17.040
But let me tell you,

22:17.150 --> 22:18.030
at your age,

22:18.070 --> 22:19.290
it's normal

22:19.430 --> 22:20.830
to have such thoughts.

22:21.660 --> 22:22.450
Then you...

22:22.750 --> 22:23.310
Then...

22:23.630 --> 22:24.590
Then what?

22:25.490 --> 22:27.150
I definitely won't agree.

22:27.750 --> 22:28.750
What are you thinking?

22:31.360 --> 22:33.260
I'm nine years older than you

22:33.670 --> 22:35.490
and you know nothing about me.

22:35.670 --> 22:36.270
As for me,

22:36.350 --> 22:37.710
I don't want to get married.

22:38.630 --> 22:39.680
Besides,

22:39.830 --> 22:40.920
I don't plan on having

22:40.940 --> 22:42.270
an intimate relationship with anyone.

22:42.910 --> 22:44.230
So I advise you

22:44.270 --> 22:45.550
to stop thinking about it.

22:49.870 --> 22:50.510
But

22:51.430 --> 22:52.650
I never

22:52.990 --> 22:54.190
told you this before.

22:54.230 --> 22:55.110
How do you know?

22:55.480 --> 22:56.220
I...

22:56.390 --> 22:57.430
Why do I feel like

22:57.510 --> 22:58.590
a kid in front of you?

23:00.230 --> 23:01.590
I teach psychology.

23:16.620 --> 23:17.930
Let me put it this way.

23:18.640 --> 23:19.440
We

23:19.470 --> 23:20.710
are from different worlds.

23:21.410 --> 23:23.360
It's impossible for us to be a couple.

23:24.030 --> 23:24.990
At most, we're just friends.

23:26.340 --> 23:27.350
Being friends is okay too.

23:28.630 --> 23:29.670
Well, your friend has been discharged.

23:30.340 --> 23:31.430
Let me treat you to a meal.

23:35.200 --> 23:35.870
Sure.

23:37.150 --> 23:37.920
I want something good.

23:38.160 --> 23:39.430
Of course we'll have the best.

23:40.830 --> 23:41.670
I'll take you to

23:41.750 --> 23:42.550
my favorite restaurant.

23:48.550 --> 23:49.540
Their food

23:49.770 --> 23:50.800
is very delicious.

23:51.910 --> 23:52.870
I used to come here at least once

23:52.910 --> 23:53.890
every week.

23:54.150 --> 23:55.620
I always came at closing

23:56.200 --> 23:56.910
when no one was around.

23:57.690 --> 23:58.510
This way, you wouldn't

23:58.550 --> 23:59.470
get spotted by fans easily,

23:59.630 --> 24:00.200
right?

24:01.590 --> 24:03.040
It's not easy for you actors.

24:04.070 --> 24:04.870
Have a seat.

24:19.430 --> 24:19.990
Sir,

24:20.430 --> 24:21.490
can you

24:21.520 --> 24:22.640
be a bit faster today?

24:22.680 --> 24:23.360
So slow.

24:23.760 --> 24:24.750
Coming.

24:25.310 --> 24:26.190
Sorry.

24:30.620 --> 24:31.310
Thank you.

24:31.310 --> 24:32.070
Sorry.

24:32.070 --> 24:32.640
Thank you.

24:32.670 --> 24:33.790
Enjoy your meal.

24:39.590 --> 24:41.330
I thought I could eat and drink

24:41.350 --> 24:42.280
something good

24:42.350 --> 24:43.310
with a superstar.

24:45.060 --> 24:46.320
You just brought me to eat noodles?

24:46.870 --> 24:48.550
Their noodles are really delicious.

24:49.160 --> 24:51.030
The owner used to run a street stall,

24:51.150 --> 24:52.550
but now he has such a big storefront.

24:52.990 --> 24:54.460
There must be a reason why.

24:54.880 --> 24:56.380
More importantly, his noodles

24:57.070 --> 24:58.270
are like what my mom made.

25:09.410 --> 25:10.400
When I was little,

25:10.480 --> 25:11.470
she always gave me

25:11.470 --> 25:12.110
her egg.

25:33.020 --> 25:33.540
So spicy.

25:34.040 --> 25:35.400
You can't eat spicy food?

25:35.870 --> 25:36.710
I can. I can.

25:37.730 --> 25:38.910
Next time, I'll tell the owner

25:38.990 --> 25:40.110
not to put peppers.

25:40.950 --> 25:41.990
But, seriously,

25:42.360 --> 25:43.380
his noodles

25:43.410 --> 25:44.980
taste different from other restaurants.

25:45.270 --> 25:46.030
Of course.

25:50.310 --> 25:50.960
When I was young,

25:50.990 --> 25:51.830
my family was poor

25:52.470 --> 25:53.570
and we didn't have air conditioning.

25:55.110 --> 25:56.140
My mom

25:56.310 --> 25:57.240
would make cold noodles

25:57.310 --> 25:58.020
in the summer

25:58.390 --> 25:59.030
to cool me down.

26:00.820 --> 26:02.330
I told my mom,

26:03.300 --> 26:04.550
"When I grow up,

26:04.590 --> 26:05.510
I'll definitely make a fortune.

26:05.990 --> 26:06.940
By then,

26:07.390 --> 26:08.520
I'll buy a big house

26:09.140 --> 26:10.330
with air conditioning in the summer

26:10.390 --> 26:11.270
and underfloor heating in the winter."

26:12.000 --> 26:12.650
Then, you could

26:12.670 --> 26:14.110
have cold noodles happily.

26:16.750 --> 26:17.310
That's great.

26:19.260 --> 26:19.970
You can't eat spicy food.

26:20.050 --> 26:20.940
Add some vinegar.

26:26.030 --> 26:26.980
More.

26:27.940 --> 26:29.200
You like vinegar this much?

26:30.440 --> 26:32.010
Girls love vinegar.

27:20.070 --> 27:20.910
Hello, what’s wrong?

27:20.930 --> 27:21.520
Mr. Wen,

27:21.590 --> 27:23.230
the PR department just contacted me.

27:23.270 --> 27:24.920
Bofeng was photographed

27:24.990 --> 27:26.030
with a woman

27:26.100 --> 27:26.790
this afternoon.

27:26.990 --> 27:28.230
The photos have already

27:28.310 --> 27:29.290
spread on the Internet.

27:29.590 --> 27:30.700
Send me the photos.

27:34.950 --> 27:35.830
[Assistant Ze]

27:44.620 --> 27:46.820
Have the PR company come to work immediately.

27:47.040 --> 27:47.950
Within half an hour,

27:47.950 --> 27:48.710
all the photos

27:48.730 --> 27:49.810
must be taken down.

27:50.310 --> 27:51.470
And then check

27:51.510 --> 27:52.540
the source of the photos.

27:52.850 --> 27:53.600
Ask them

27:53.630 --> 27:55.350
how much they want and pay them.

27:55.370 --> 27:56.070
Okay, Mr. Wen.

27:56.410 --> 27:58.130
[Outpatient]

27:58.230 --> 27:59.110
Check this information

27:59.110 --> 27:59.960
later.

27:59.990 --> 28:01.510
I think you should check on

28:01.510 --> 28:02.290
Bed 19 more.

28:02.320 --> 28:03.940
Make sure he changes the dressing promptly.

28:04.070 --> 28:04.550
Take a look.

28:04.710 --> 28:05.040
Okay.

28:05.070 --> 28:05.910
I'll confirm it.

28:06.030 --> 28:06.550
Yes.

28:06.590 --> 28:08.530
He just got the anesthesia.

28:08.870 --> 28:10.020
Check on him more.

28:10.050 --> 28:10.670
Okay.

28:10.750 --> 28:11.600
Lu Yan.

28:15.550 --> 28:17.070
Are you free?

28:17.090 --> 28:18.700
I have something to tell you.

28:21.210 --> 28:22.080
Sure.

28:25.990 --> 28:26.790
You resigned?

28:30.990 --> 28:32.210
I plan to

28:32.830 --> 28:34.000
leave Ninghai.

28:35.590 --> 28:36.470
Is it

28:37.110 --> 28:38.110
because of Ding Jing?

28:41.190 --> 28:41.740
No.

28:42.630 --> 28:44.150
Actually, Uncle and Auntie

28:44.590 --> 28:47.070
are willing to help us.

28:48.910 --> 28:50.850
But I don't want to live

28:51.550 --> 28:53.230
by receiving favors anymore.

28:55.750 --> 28:57.670
Actually, I've followed

28:58.830 --> 29:00.390
Ding Jing since college

29:01.580 --> 29:02.800
because she could give me

29:02.830 --> 29:03.790
a lot of benefits.

29:05.150 --> 29:06.540
She even found me my job.

29:07.630 --> 29:08.600
But

29:09.430 --> 29:10.390
I thought about it.

29:11.670 --> 29:13.840
It seems that I've never tried

29:13.870 --> 29:15.070
to venture out on my own.

29:18.190 --> 29:20.830
Maybe I'll be better than before.

29:24.710 --> 29:25.430
I believe you.

29:27.910 --> 29:29.270
You'll be better than now.

29:35.950 --> 29:36.630
Lu Yan,

29:38.230 --> 29:40.820
there is something

29:42.190 --> 29:42.950
I've been hesitant

29:42.950 --> 29:43.830
to tell you.

29:47.670 --> 29:48.710
But I thought that

29:49.070 --> 29:50.710
since I’m leaving,

29:51.550 --> 29:52.390
I'll tell you

29:52.410 --> 29:53.390
everything now.

29:59.060 --> 30:00.400
Actually, back then,

30:01.550 --> 30:03.220
I knew a little about

30:05.130 --> 30:06.550
Ding Jing and Deng Man back then.

30:15.010 --> 30:15.670
I knew

30:15.710 --> 30:17.130
you're sensible.

30:17.520 --> 30:18.550
It's good.

30:18.810 --> 30:19.920
Don't worry.

30:20.240 --> 30:22.140
Once this is done,

30:22.190 --> 30:23.430
I will destroy all the videos

30:23.480 --> 30:24.910
in front of you.

30:25.600 --> 30:26.880
What do you want me to do?

30:27.760 --> 30:28.960
It's very simple.

30:29.750 --> 30:31.120
If you have time,

30:31.150 --> 30:33.380
go to the basketball court more often.

30:33.400 --> 30:35.100
Watch Jiang Chengyi play basketball

30:35.790 --> 30:37.920
and slowly alienate Lu Yan.

30:38.220 --> 30:39.340
Find a chance

30:39.600 --> 30:41.410
and have her give Jiang Chengyi to you.

30:44.000 --> 30:45.120
If Lu Yan

30:45.150 --> 30:47.270
is shameless and refuses,

30:47.360 --> 30:49.530
you should confess to Jiang Chengyi.

30:50.710 --> 30:52.020
Do you understand?

31:05.600 --> 31:06.970
What do you want for dinner?

31:06.990 --> 31:08.370
I'll treat you to something expensive.

31:09.190 --> 31:09.920
What made you

31:09.940 --> 31:11.310
so happy?

31:12.080 --> 31:12.710
By the way,

31:12.740 --> 31:14.300
what were you two talking about?

31:14.340 --> 31:17.520
Isn't she Lu Yan's good friend?

31:17.760 --> 31:18.670
Good friend?

31:21.380 --> 31:22.870
Then Lu Yan's good days

31:22.890 --> 31:24.170
are coming to an end.

31:26.270 --> 31:27.370
Why?

31:27.390 --> 31:28.760
Because she and Jiang Chengyi

31:28.780 --> 31:30.300
are about to break up.

31:31.200 --> 31:32.660
What do you mean?

31:33.550 --> 31:34.310
Did you think of

31:34.310 --> 31:35.430
a good idea?

31:36.410 --> 31:38.050
I won't have to do anything this time.

31:39.140 --> 31:40.650
She'll handle it for me.

31:43.510 --> 31:44.440
She...

31:44.980 --> 31:46.330
You mean

31:46.480 --> 31:47.190
Deng Man?

31:49.370 --> 31:51.240
Why her?

31:55.040 --> 31:56.170
Because...

31:58.460 --> 32:00.680
she has an unspeakable secret.

32:05.150 --> 32:05.850
Come on.

32:05.880 --> 32:06.970
What are you waiting for?

32:09.760 --> 32:10.660
Jing.

32:12.120 --> 32:13.690
Do you know what happened?

32:13.710 --> 32:15.130
How would I know?

32:15.160 --> 32:16.800
Just say it.

32:16.820 --> 32:17.520
Deng Man

32:18.520 --> 32:19.610
committed suicide.

32:23.070 --> 32:24.000
What do you mean?

32:24.020 --> 32:25.230
Deng Man committed suicide!

32:25.270 --> 32:25.870
She...

32:25.900 --> 32:27.920
She... She's dead.

32:30.450 --> 32:30.920
Dead?

32:30.950 --> 32:31.470
Jing.

32:31.490 --> 32:32.260
Did you say something

32:32.290 --> 32:33.340
to her that day?

32:33.430 --> 32:34.710
I saw you talking to her.

32:34.730 --> 32:35.510
Why would I

32:35.550 --> 32:36.660
talk to her?

32:36.760 --> 32:38.670
I'm warning you. Don't talk nonsense.

32:39.180 --> 32:40.380
Jing, where are you going?

32:40.440 --> 32:41.290
Jing.

32:43.030 --> 32:43.980
Hello, Dad.

32:44.030 --> 32:45.560
Pick me up!

32:47.320 --> 32:49.530
Actually, I heard

32:50.310 --> 32:51.930
what they said.

32:52.930 --> 32:55.470
But I didn't dare to tell Ding Jing.

32:56.790 --> 32:57.600
Later,

32:57.990 --> 32:59.440
I didn't dare to tell you either.

32:59.730 --> 33:00.790
Why?

33:02.130 --> 33:04.380
When we were at school,

33:05.330 --> 33:06.320
at the beginning,

33:06.640 --> 33:08.330
Ding Jing forced me

33:08.390 --> 33:09.540
to bully Deng Man.

33:09.990 --> 33:11.060
But later,

33:11.080 --> 33:13.050
to make Ding Jing happy,

33:14.190 --> 33:15.910
I also took the initiative

33:15.950 --> 33:17.190
to bully Deng Man.

33:21.240 --> 33:22.110
Clean it up.

33:23.990 --> 33:24.580
Okay.

33:28.110 --> 33:29.590
I really hate

33:29.640 --> 33:30.790
how I was.

33:32.990 --> 33:33.830
So,

33:35.190 --> 33:36.350
I decided to make this secret

33:36.430 --> 33:38.030
rot inside me.

33:39.140 --> 33:40.800
But you saved me.

33:41.230 --> 33:42.320
I know

33:42.430 --> 33:43.800
you really want to know

33:43.830 --> 33:45.780
the truth of Deng Man's suicide.

33:51.740 --> 33:52.870
If I

33:54.310 --> 33:55.520
had a good friend like you,

33:55.550 --> 33:57.070
that would be great.

34:04.890 --> 34:06.000
Friends

34:06.000 --> 34:07.150
cherish each other.

34:11.810 --> 34:12.790
Anything else?

34:13.080 --> 34:14.139
Tell me everything.

34:14.630 --> 34:15.590
What was in the video?

34:15.670 --> 34:16.670
What secret?

34:17.270 --> 34:18.510
I really don't know

34:18.510 --> 34:19.960
anything else.

34:20.280 --> 34:21.510
If Ding Jing didn't want to tell me,

34:21.590 --> 34:23.570
I wouldn't take the initiative to ask either.

34:23.790 --> 34:26.110
I didn't want to get myself involved.

34:26.739 --> 34:27.780
What about Ding Jing?

34:28.830 --> 34:29.830
What else did she know?

34:30.469 --> 34:32.150
I don't think she knew anything else.

34:33.560 --> 34:34.960
Ding Jing has died.

34:35.550 --> 34:36.429
I have nothing

34:36.429 --> 34:37.510
to hide now.

34:44.510 --> 34:45.150
Lu Yan.

34:48.270 --> 34:49.159
I'm sorry.

35:10.700 --> 35:11.240
Senior.

35:11.270 --> 35:11.830
You're back.

35:11.990 --> 35:12.470
You’re back.

35:12.470 --> 35:12.940
Captain Jiang.

35:12.970 --> 35:13.520
Captain Jiang.

35:13.870 --> 35:14.390
Captain Jiang.

35:14.570 --> 35:15.260
Captain Jiang.

35:15.930 --> 35:17.050
You’re back at the right time.

35:18.120 --> 35:18.930
Look at this.

35:18.950 --> 35:19.770
What's wrong?

35:20.950 --> 35:22.510
We just checked

35:22.550 --> 35:24.190
Ding Jing's call records again.

35:24.540 --> 35:25.560
We discovered that before,

35:25.590 --> 35:26.800
we always put our attention

35:26.830 --> 35:27.960
in the three days before

35:27.990 --> 35:28.950
and after her murder.

35:29.510 --> 35:30.190
Just now,

35:30.190 --> 35:31.150
Liu Hao expanded the range

35:31.310 --> 35:32.810
and found a number

35:33.510 --> 35:35.040
that Ding Jing also contacted.

35:35.630 --> 35:40.460
[Zhou Zhicheng]

35:37.400 --> 35:38.220
Coach Zhou.

35:41.270 --> 35:43.240
So Ding Jing

35:43.270 --> 35:44.310
used a video

35:44.310 --> 35:45.350
to threaten Deng Man.

35:46.720 --> 35:48.070
Video. Want water?

35:48.550 --> 35:49.230
Do you know

35:49.230 --> 35:50.150
what the content was?

35:50.200 --> 35:50.790
No.

35:50.830 --> 35:51.630
Liu Yujie doesn’t know

35:51.630 --> 35:52.680
what it is either.

35:54.290 --> 35:54.870
According to

35:54.870 --> 35:55.870
our previous experience,

35:55.910 --> 35:57.230
female college students

35:58.440 --> 36:00.140
are usually threatened

36:00.160 --> 36:02.020
by sexual videos.

36:02.940 --> 36:03.820
But did Deng Man

36:03.880 --> 36:04.950
have this problem?

36:05.030 --> 36:05.750
Or,

36:05.870 --> 36:07.350
could Deng Man have been

36:07.510 --> 36:08.750
threatened with anything else?

36:08.900 --> 36:09.760
Do you know?

36:09.870 --> 36:11.110
I can't think of anything

36:11.230 --> 36:12.870
even if you ask me to.

36:17.630 --> 36:18.410
I have a question.

36:18.870 --> 36:21.070
Have you been in touch with Coach Zhou lately?

36:21.190 --> 36:22.340
Coach Zhou?

36:22.710 --> 36:24.110
I looked for him once before.

36:24.630 --> 36:25.430
When?

36:25.590 --> 36:26.240
Well...

36:27.510 --> 36:28.630
When we quarreled

36:28.710 --> 36:29.820
at the library.

36:30.110 --> 36:31.150
After reading "Hiroshima Mon Amour,"

36:31.150 --> 36:32.510
I thought

36:32.750 --> 36:34.630
to ask him about Deng Man.

36:34.870 --> 36:35.590
In the end...

36:40.320 --> 36:41.080
What did he say?

36:41.800 --> 36:43.280
He said

36:44.930 --> 36:46.760
Deng Man confessed to you before.

36:47.510 --> 36:49.060
Deng Man confessed to me?

36:50.460 --> 36:51.790
Why didn't I know?

36:51.870 --> 36:53.520
That's what he told me.

36:56.880 --> 36:57.710
Deng Man and I

36:57.710 --> 36:59.390
only met a few times before.

37:00.510 --> 37:01.550
Once, she came to find me

37:01.550 --> 37:02.520
when I

37:03.030 --> 37:03.790
returned to the dorm.

37:04.680 --> 37:05.630
Jiang Chengyi.

37:07.110 --> 37:08.180
What are you doing here?

37:09.330 --> 37:10.610
I need to talk to you.

37:11.030 --> 37:11.550
Go ahead.

37:21.270 --> 37:22.010
Tell me.

37:25.460 --> 37:27.000
Are you looking for Lu Yan?

37:29.990 --> 37:31.110
I don't want to see her.

37:33.230 --> 37:34.470
Did you two fight?

37:38.130 --> 37:39.260
What happened then?

37:43.940 --> 37:44.630
Well...

37:45.190 --> 37:46.070
Come on. I'll walk you back.

37:46.070 --> 37:46.470
Let's go.

37:46.530 --> 37:47.490
No need.

37:48.670 --> 37:50.200
Go back.

37:50.670 --> 37:51.160
By the way,

37:51.190 --> 37:52.510
don't tell her

37:52.630 --> 37:54.080
I came to you today.

37:55.950 --> 37:57.110
But she didn't manage

37:57.150 --> 37:58.190
to say anything.

38:00.920 --> 38:02.250
Then what do you mean?

38:02.400 --> 38:03.350
Do you think

38:05.190 --> 38:06.470
Coach Zhou is lying?

38:08.070 --> 38:09.230
I don't know either.

38:10.260 --> 38:11.810
I'll find a chance to ask him.

38:19.420 --> 38:21.200
[What old hag is that? She's not good enough for our Bofeng.]

38:21.280 --> 38:23.700
[This is a big scandal. A mysterious woman on a date with Yu Bofeng.]

38:24.770 --> 38:25.820
A bowl of noodles

38:25.840 --> 38:27.520
made me lose at least five million yuan.

38:29.950 --> 38:30.510
I didn't expect

38:30.590 --> 38:31.990
things would be so serious.

38:35.090 --> 38:36.760
Peng, it's all my fault.

38:37.320 --> 38:38.550
I'm hold a press conference.

38:38.580 --> 38:39.400
I'll apologize.

38:39.920 --> 38:41.030
I'll bear the loss

38:41.070 --> 38:42.430
to the company.

38:44.750 --> 38:45.660
Do you think I want you

38:45.660 --> 38:46.500
to compensate me?

38:47.510 --> 38:48.430
How to save you

38:48.470 --> 38:49.590
is what I care about the most.

38:55.310 --> 38:56.400
As for the photos,

38:56.470 --> 38:57.870
I'll have the PR company handle it.

38:58.040 --> 38:58.670
Your resources

38:58.710 --> 38:59.670
may have some losses.

38:59.690 --> 39:00.790
I'll try my best

39:00.910 --> 39:01.870
to minimize losses.

39:01.980 --> 39:04.350
What you should do now is listen to me.

39:04.600 --> 39:06.070
Go home and sleep.

39:07.390 --> 39:08.690
Sorry, Peng.

39:09.470 --> 39:10.430
Sorry for the trouble.

39:13.290 --> 39:14.200
If you really feel

39:14.230 --> 39:15.230
sorry toward me,

39:15.400 --> 39:16.310
don't contact her

39:16.310 --> 39:17.070
for the time being.

39:17.150 --> 39:18.280
We'll talk about it later.

39:21.380 --> 39:22.450
Give me your phone.

39:24.050 --> 39:25.070
Just a few days.

39:25.150 --> 39:26.290
When the attention is over,

39:26.350 --> 39:27.790
you can contact her however you want.

39:42.460 --> 39:44.260
I’ll go back now.

39:56.030 --> 39:56.550
Mr. Wen.

39:56.980 --> 39:57.670
You called me?

39:58.990 --> 39:59.680
Tell Hao to

39:59.710 --> 40:00.590
keep an eye on him 24 hours a day.

40:00.830 --> 40:01.710
Don't let him run around.

40:02.350 --> 40:03.050
Got it.

40:08.020 --> 40:09.790
[Zhou Zhicheng of Ninghai University received Ninghai Model Citizen Award]

40:09.790 --> 40:11.210
[Zhou Zhicheng Wins 9th Ninghai Track Meet]

40:16.950 --> 40:18.990
He has cancer?

40:22.870 --> 40:23.900
[Headlines] [News] [Hot Topics]

40:24.520 --> 40:26.280
[Zhou Zhicheng]

40:26.380 --> 40:30.790
[Fight Against Cancer, Model Husband: Story Behind Coach Zhou Zhicheng]

40:37.420 --> 40:38.380
So early?

40:39.840 --> 40:40.740
Sun.

40:43.270 --> 40:44.550
Let me ask you something.

40:44.940 --> 40:45.630
Did you work

40:45.670 --> 40:46.870
in the tumor department

40:46.890 --> 40:47.660
for a while?

40:49.350 --> 40:50.170
Yes.

40:51.100 --> 40:52.470
They sent me there to learn

40:52.490 --> 40:53.840
for more than half a year.

40:54.390 --> 40:54.920
What's wrong?

40:58.840 --> 41:00.480
Can you check a case for me?

41:00.850 --> 41:02.660
The patient's name is Zhou Zhicheng.

41:06.550 --> 41:07.320
I found him.

41:12.910 --> 41:15.420
This patient is quite rich.

41:15.890 --> 41:17.210
They're all imported medicines.

41:17.630 --> 41:18.480
Yes.

41:17.700 --> 41:24.010
[Three times a day] [Twice a day]

41:18.500 --> 41:20.120
You can't afford this without

41:20.150 --> 41:20.990
a few hundred thousand a year.
